    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white leading-tight">The self-hosted Slack alternative</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Same features you love. No per-seat pricing. No data on someone else's servers. Enzyme gives your team a home for chat that you actually own.</p>
